ge-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/vtuber_agency_774inc_will_merge_all_the_groups_under_umbrella_and_changes_name.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/vtuber_agency_774inc_will_merge_all_the_groups_under_umbrella_and_changes_name.jpg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/vtuber_agency_774inc_will_merge_all_the_groups_under_umbrella_and_changes_name.jpg" alt="VTuber办公室774inc.旗下所有团体将被整合并更名为“Nanashinku”" class="wp-image-87464"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2019 774inc。</figcaption></figure><p> 3月21日，原774inc.合并了原来的附属集团，并更名为现在的Nanashi Inc.。 <a href="https://p2y.jp/774inc-nanashiinku-new-vtubers-amaui-ina-uruu-and-hinata-mashu-make-their-debut/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="新人也登场">新艺人也出道了</a>，但另一方面， <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-774inc-nanashiinku-apologized-for-quality-degradation-of-live-event-due-to-inadequacies-on-the-part-of-management/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="举办现场活动时遇到的麻烦">举办现场活动出现了问题</a>， <a href="https://p2y.jp/774inc-nanashiinku-vtuber-seshima-rui-announces-cancellation-of-birthday-live-and-suspension-of-activities/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="妹岛芮的活动暂停。">妹岛芮的活动暂停</a>， <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-graduated-from-774inc-nanashiinku-and-became-independent/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="索帕特拉的独立">帕托拉索独立</a>，和<a href="https://p2y.jp/774inc-nanashiinku-vtuber-fuma-wat-to-graduate-on-april-25/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="和都风马毕业">藤风麻毕业</a>， <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-oura-rukako-suspends-talent-activities-indefinitely-and-becomes-a-774inc-nanashiinku-management-staff-member/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="大浦流花子的艺人活动无限期暂停。">大浦佳子的艺人活动无限期暂停。</a>由于重叠，我们有收到了关心接下来会发生什么的观众和粉丝的反馈。</p><p>看看 Nanashinku 未来能否恢复，将会很有趣。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embe